  "headline": "Risk Management",
  "description": "Risk management identifies, assesses, and mitigates threats to an organization's capital and earnings. Process: identify risk → analyze (probability × impact) → evaluate → treat (avoid, reduce, transfer/insure, accept). Financial risk: market, credit, liquidity, operational. Enterprise Risk Management (ERM) takes a holistic approach.",
